Package: manuscript
Title: Tools to Assist Statistical Report Writing
Version: 0.0.0.9000
Authors@R: 
    person("Qiong", "Chen", , "chenq08@126.com", role = c("aut", "cre", "ctb", "cph"))
Description: Provides tools to assist statistical report writing through the automated
    generation and management of analysis and reporting projects using RStudio
    Project workflows. The package enables the creation of standardized directory
    structures, Quarto (`.qmd`) documents, and README files, supporting reproducible
    and efficient report preparation.
